title: Classical Trumpet Concertos - Sheet Music & Audio
description:
This is a collection of both the SHEET MUSIC and the MP3 AUDIO files of three concertos for classical trumpet. 

Franz Joseph Haydn - Trumpet Concerto in E-flat
Johann Nepomuk Hummel - Trumpet Concerto in E-flat
J. G. Neruda - Trumpet Concerto in E-flat

The sheet music for each piece is in PDF format and includes the piano score and parts for both trumpet in B-flat and trumpet in E-flat. 

The audio files are high quality 256kps encoded with Lame MP3Pro. The performance is by Ole' Edvard Antonsen. 

These concerti are important works for the instrument and standard repertoire for any student or professional.
